// SimpleChip.cbp DEMO
new Wire
new Wire
new Wire
new Wire
pop TMP
pop A
pop B
pop OUT
map A 2
map B 3
map OUT 4
new PMOS
new PMOS
pop G_1
pop G_2
new Wire
new Wire
pop VSS
pop VDD
map VSS 0
map VDD 1
link G_1 VSS SOURCE
link G_2 A CONTROL
link G_1 B CONTROL
link G_2 OUT DRAIN
link G_2 TMP SOURCE
link G_1 TMP DRAIN
lock